      "message": "Line 67: isPluginOverwrite requires OriginalBody to be truthy, so a valid plugin change from an empty original message to a non-empty Body will not be detected and the user cannot toggle back to the original. Use an explicit null/undefined check instead of truthiness so empty strings remain valid original values.\n```suggestion\nproperty bool hasOriginalBody: OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d undefined \u0026\u0026 OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d null\nproperty bool isPluginOverwrite: hasOriginalBody \u0026\u0026 Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody\n```",
