      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 80: Returning OriginalBody directly bypasses the existing MessagesAdapter.parseMessage path used for Body. That can make the original-message view inconsistent with normal messages: links, previews, emoji/markup handling, and any escaping/sanitization performed by parseMessage will not apply. Store and render a parsed original body, or invoke the same parsing path for OriginalBody before displaying it.\n```suggestion\nif (showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite) {\n    MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(Id + \"-original\", OriginalBody, UtilsAdapter.getAppValue(Settings.DisplayHyperlinkPreviews), rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\n    return ParsedOriginalBody;\n}\n```",
